      "value": "<p>You have mastered techniques to take advantage of every drop in any enemy's guard, gaining the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>When you hit a creature with an opportunity attack, the creature's speed becomes 0 for the rest of the turn.</li>\n<li>Creatures provoke opportunity attacks from you even if they take the Disengage action before leaving your reach.</li>\n<li>You can take an opportunity attack against a creature within your reach when they make an attack against a target other than you (and that target doesn't have this feat).</li>\n</ul>",
